      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WRECK IT REX (1) stuck on well last time to finish 1.3 lengths back in second (23.13) at The Gardens in a Grade 5 over 400m. Must come into calculations. ZIPPING ODESSA (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing eighth (23.40) in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. MARVIN MONELLI (7) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (20.65) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from three starts. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. ZARA GO ON (2) is worth a look over a shorter trip this time.",
